## Welcome to my GitHub page.
To view the presentation on my Freshmen Advising Resource (_FAR_) please download the files using the links above and either view the Powerpoint Show (.ppsx) or the PDF (.pdf) file. Please contact me at [hilgert@email.arizona.edu](hilgert@email.arizona.edu) with any feedback you may have.
